name: Cantina Brawl
Lore: '''...watch your step. This place can be a little rough.'' The Mos Eisley Cantina harbors smugglers, thieves, cutthroats, criminals and bounty hunters!',
Text: 'Use 2 Force to cause a fight to break out in the Cantina. Both players draw destiny. All characters in Cantina with an ability number matching either destiny draw are lost.',
